  "title": "I could not find what I was looking for",
  "body": "Hi! I have a documentation issue on InstantSearch.js, I could not find what I was looking for which is: how to use the render function in the [refinementList widget](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/widgets/refinementList.html#struct-Widget)\r\n\r\nFrom my understanding in the docs, this is what I should do:\r\n\r\n```\r\nsearch.addWidget(\r\n        instantsearch.widgets.refinementList({\r\n          container: '#tags-filter',\r\n          attributeName: 'categories',\r\n          render: function(foo){\r\n            console.log(foo);\r\n          }\r\n        })\r\n      );\r\n```\r\n\r\nHowever the render method is never executed.\r\n\r\nThank you 🙂",
